fulltitle: Domestic Intelligence & JFK's Murder: Mark Lane and Tim Butz
title: Domestic Intelligence & JFK's Murder: Mark Lane and Tim Butz
_filename: _Domestic Intelligence & JFK's Murder - Mark Lane and Tim Butz.webm
description:
For more related content, please visit: https://archive.org/details/@altviewstv-fanclub

Tim Butz, Editor of CounterSpy Magazine, and Mark Lane, Civil Rights attorney and author of Rush to Judgement, discuss the domestic intelligence operations of the FBI and the CIA, including COINTELPRO and attempts to shut down criticism of the Warren Commission.
